skdetail:

Invocation Name: hike master
des: The skill provides good hikes around Bay Area. It works with the invocation call "Alexa, ask Hike Master" . A sample phase to use is "Alexa, ask hike master to give me a hike that is easy"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
